<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Algorithm for Data Encryption Standard</h1>
        <p>This demo illustrates the Data Encryption Standard (DES) algorithm. You can input a message and a key, and specify the number of encryption steps to see the intermediate encrypted messages.</p>

        <div id="control-panel">
            <div>
                <label for="input-message">message</label>
                <input type="text" id="input-message" value="hello">
            </div>
