    <title>Deformation Pattern in an Earthquake Source Region</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        #control-panel {
